      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# BrainDead - SAM3 Parts Segmentation\n\nOpen-vocabulary part segmentation from a single image. SAM3 segments each named prompt into a mask; the Parts pipeline crops each part to its own RGBA image and exports per-part PNGs + a layered composite.\n\n## Flow\n1. **Load Image** - pick any image (subject on a clean background works best).\n2. **BD SAM3 Multi-Prompt** - type one part name per line in `prompts`. Standalone: auto-downloads the official `Comfy-Org/sam3.1` checkpoint on first use. Outputs `per_prompt_masks` + `combined_mask`.\n3. **BD Parts Builder** - crops/pads each masked region into its own image, emits a `PARTS_BUNDLE`.\n4. **BD Parts Compose** - flattens the parts back into a single preview image (shown inline).\n5. **BD Parts Export** - writes per-part RGBA PNGs + a composite PNG to the output folder.\n\n## Models / VRAM\nSAM3 (`Comfy-Org/sam3.1`) auto-downloads in-house on first run - no comfyui-rmbg needed. Plan ~8-10 GB VRAM for the SAM3 model + text encoder. Edit the `prompts` list to match your subject (e.g. `head`, `torso`, `arm`, `leg`, `hand`).\n\n---\n**BrainDeadGuild** - created by **BizaNator**\n[BrainDeadGuild.com](https://BrainDeadGuild.com) · [BrainDead.TV](https://BrainDead.TV) · [GitHub](https://github.com/BizaNator/ComfyUI-BrainDead) · [Discord](https://braindeadguild.com/discord)\n"
      ],
      "title": "ℹ️ About — BrainDead SAM3 Parts"
    },
